WEBVTT

00:00:58.081 --> 00:01:03.179
Shu bilan birga epidemiyalar oldini olish
uchun esa juda kam pul ajratmoqdamiz.

00:01:04.129 --> 00:01:07.093
Biz keyingi epidemiya tarqalishiga
tayyor emasmiz.

00:01:08.023 --> 00:01:09.758
Masalan, Ebola virusini olsak.

00:01:09.758 --> 00:01:13.615
Aminmanki, hammangiz bu haqda
gazetalarda o'qigansiz -

00:01:13.615 --> 00:01:15.221
u juda ko'p muammolar olib keldi.

00:01:15.221 --> 00:01:18.876
Men uni poliomelitning yo'qolishini 
analiz qilishda qo'llanilgan usullar

00:01:18.876 --> 00:01:23.721
yordamida diqqat bilan kuzatib bordim.

00:01:23.721 --> 00:01:25.573
Bunday bir holatda,

00:01:25.573 --> 00:01:30.081
muammo - tizimning 
yaxshi ishlamasligida emas,